Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:45.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:48.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the front desk, \Nwith your wake-up call!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:50.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:52.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:54.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice day, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:29.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:44.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Center City.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:02:59.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the welcome party coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:04.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already proceeded to phase two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:06.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been no oversights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against the Ghost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:10.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure not to get yourself haunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:16.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the road repair erases the footprints,\NI want to go check it out myself once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:19.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll proceed with the \Nsteamroller plan right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:20.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don't be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have two or three things I'm curious about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:27.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up the invitation until I've \Ndetermined them one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:30.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Agent Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked out on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Heroman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:45.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kinda embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:51.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, wait! The guy needs to \Ntake the lead on a date, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where Lina would enjoy going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Heroman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:02.61,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,The barricade is set to be \Nlifted at eight o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.26,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,#3 filming is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.72,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceeding to precision measurements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.72,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing out of the ordinary detected \Nin a 30 meter square perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where the trail cuts off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Onesy, twosy, threesy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:35.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it... I'd better \Nput in some work or else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:40.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Coming, coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Show your true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:03.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, it's me! Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:08.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother is a tiny munchkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:11.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I grew a bit in four years!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:15.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:19.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I caught the alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:21.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:29.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were touring with \Nyour band on the east coast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:35.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Center City was attacked by \Naliens so I came runnin' all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:39.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three months since then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:43.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have the money to \Nget here so quick, sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:44.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, it's a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:48.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're old enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:50.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd have at least called...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:56.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, that would have been a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing things at her own pace, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:02.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:04.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:06.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Five lumps of sugar, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:11.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came running here, but what a letdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:14.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There ain't any aliens around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:17.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened three months ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always like this, Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:23.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Egocentric and selfish... You never \Ncare at all about the people around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:26.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I came all this way so \NI ain't leavin' right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:29.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably crash here two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I hate the west coast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:46.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Minami. We have a request for a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:48.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:50.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They say they're someone with the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:54.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems they wish to tell \Nyou the details only in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:58.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three months since we've \Nbeen helping the reconstruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What took them so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:04.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:05.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:13.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my favorite, limited time \Nonly, pumpkin flavored cereal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you care, I ain't eating that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:16.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:19.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being such a nag. That ain't cool, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got in the shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna clean off after the trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:31.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You go after me. I'm first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How does that work exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, why are you stripping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just shower together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:40.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:42.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving right now, \Nso keep your clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:46.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal? We used to \Ndo this all the time, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:49.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in middle school now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock before you enter, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:06.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But yeah, I see you still \Ntreasure this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:11.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's helmet is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go wearing it around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! You and your father complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:19.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, you sleep in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:23.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan on making a lady sleep on the sofa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:25.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This room is now mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:33.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always, always taking my...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:32.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:39.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Anything but that, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:42.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I won't break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:47.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, do you remember how much of \Nmy stuff you've broken before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't break 'em. They just broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:53.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... Caring so much about \Na stupid toy at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:54.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:58.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Joey, how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing looks pretty expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:04.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think we could get some cash by selling it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even joke about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman isn't a toy, or something to be sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it, he's your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:24.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:27.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Joey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:28.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To Psy's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time we've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:44.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Agent Hughes from the National \NIntelligence Agency, abbreviated NIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Dr. Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:52.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the NIA?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:58.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what does the agency under direct \Ncontrol of the President want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:02.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want the MR-1 to be formally \Nadopted into the military, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:04.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid it's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:09.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like your advice on a certain \Ncase we're investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:13.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or more precisely, to hear your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:14.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:20.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And I would like for you to \Ncooperate with us on this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:27.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are an agency that answers \Ndirectly to the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:31.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a very deep connection \Nwith your clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying this is for my own good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:42.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I will write \Nall the reports myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:45.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:49.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if you'll allow me to ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:53.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Ask whatever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At the request of the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:59.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,or rather you used your great \Npower as one close to the military
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:04.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to join in and aid the government's \Nreconstruction in a grand way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:09.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This was designed as a demonstration \Nof your robot, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:15.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that was the point, there are more \Nprominent places, like near the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to be frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:26.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here in Center City?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:41.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:45.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That nightmare has returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just great...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:51.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'd better steer clear \Nof your house for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:54.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's only been here half a \Nday and I'm already worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:56.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a disaster, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's only just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Holly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:06.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been four years since \Nshe suddenly left town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all coming back to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:15.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That dark period in our youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:26.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Always pickin' a fight, rude, strong as \Nheck, buttin' in at the wrong time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:30.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you callin' beautiful, \Nelegant, and graceful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:39.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:41.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:42.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:45.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I have a favor to ask you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:49.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you do it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:58.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I will contact \Nyou again in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:04.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cunning bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:10.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I not be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:15.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In just one night the entire \Npile of wreckage was cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Any clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were I'd go and\Nthank to guy myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:23.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:26.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to them our schedule and \Nbudget is looking much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:28.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's there to complain about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:33.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd like to get back to work, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One final question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:41.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person do you \Nthink this individual is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An ally of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around here thinks so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ally of justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:58.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... So you just wanted \Nus to show you around town?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:03.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You leave for a bit and\Neverything changes in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:07.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, where do you \Nwant us to show you, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:09.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A place with a lot of people, if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:13.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And a place where it won't \Nmatter if I stick out a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:16.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complainin' and find a place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Any results?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:25.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up questioning people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't get any proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we should go one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:32.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing that's peaked my interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still only in the realm of conjecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:39.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but all the incidents of the Ghost\Nhave the same characteristic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think of something, Agent Hughes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:46.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Just a bit of an \Nopening act for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are we going to go on like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:55.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask that to my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off a big firework right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:05.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? An explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:11.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems there are some people left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:15.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:19.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That giant sphere destroyed this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The foundation isn't doing so well, so \Nthe rescue squads can't get to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you going to do, Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:30.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You could probably use Heroman \Nto save them, but today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two standin' around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:35.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:42.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Psy, I've been entrusted with a \Ngreat duty to protect Center City.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back soon, so handle things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Joey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Psy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:59.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The accident happened above here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:25.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Engage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the people that were left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:42.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been searching for you a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:46.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally meet, Mr. Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:49.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been searching for Heroman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:52.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for tricking \Nyou into coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't think I could \Nmeet you any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:17:00.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, there are no people nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:02.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That means this is a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:05.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So the people being left behind was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:09.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot of things I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:11.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About your relationship with the Skrugg,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:15.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the large amount of volunteer \Nwork you've been doing lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:21.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But first... May I ask you what you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:26.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:29.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps you cannot speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:30.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. I have to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:35.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me. Let me introduce myself first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:39.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am from the NIA, an agency that \Nanswers directly to the President...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:40.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:46.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, we're not done talking yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, crap, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:18:00.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I was finally going to show my stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the main guest goes \Nwandering off somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:10.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:14.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:19.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:29.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a shortcut through the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:43.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:52.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At least listen to my whole introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:54.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:55.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go leaving your cute \Nsister and wandering off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:00.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:02.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:07.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and get back so I can start!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Start?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:36.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does the clear blue sky know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:47.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does even the kind wind know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:53.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right or left, going either \Nway it's the same anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:59.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't got no map...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:05.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the sky'll point out, like sproutin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:10.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stretch out my hand, I \Nshould be able to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:16.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to bloom, \Nlike dandelion fluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:23.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wander, I'll be able \Nto find it, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:27.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gently...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:33.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At the base of the rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Holly's gotten really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Sis! You're sure to be \Na big star with a song like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:58.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard to save up money and \Nsee you perform on stage sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:02.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you heading to \Nnext? The east coast again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:05.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think I'll stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:11.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something interesting in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:24.09,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"Can you hear this voice?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:31.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been calling that, always, from deep within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:45.46,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you, all alone, let another lonely one be next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:51.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because together it's not lonely, it's twoly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:56.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you're not alone any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:22:59.99,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because there's no one next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:02.54,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't mean that I'm lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:07.74,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone to notice this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:13.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,that heart must have surely cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:16.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we'll crush to bits
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.65,0:23:20.35,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the fortress of our limitless sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:24.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:27.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? I'm running through at full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:31.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,To where you're waiting, left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:34.64,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,in the place of tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:39.77,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you, with burning passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:43.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:53.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Heroman:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:57.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why won't everyone leave us alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:23:58.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:01.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina wants to get closer to Joey,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.87,0:24:04.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so she successfully asked Joey out on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:11.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However a new threat appears \Nand gets in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.23,0:24:16.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Heroman #12: Stalkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.03,0:24:18.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.66,0:24:20.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
